Vulpes Hires Titan Capital’s Chuang for Volatility Hedge Fund

-- B y   N e t t y   I s m a i l
-- 
2011-05-23T08:02:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-23/vulpes-hires-titan-capital-s-chuang-for-volatility-hedge-fund.html
Vulpes Investment Management Pte said
it hired Kyle Chuang as portfolio manager focusing on its LAVA
volatility fund.  Chuang joins the Singapore-based firm from Titan Capital
Group in  Hong Kong , where he was responsible for the New York-
based hedge fund firm’s Titan Asia Volatility Fund, Vulpes said
in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Netty Ismail in  Singapore  
 nismail3@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andreea Papuc at 
 apapuc1@bloomberg.net  